  "keyFeatures": [
    "1.1 billion trading records from Polymarket's inception to present across 268K+ markets",
    "Direct data access from Polygon blockchain via RPC — no third-party dependencies",
    "5 analysis-ready Parquet datasets: orderfilled, trades, markets, quant, users",
    "Real-time continuous mode that syncs new data every 2 seconds",
    "Resume support with auto-save checkpoints — restart without data loss",
    "Efficient Parquet storage with Snappy compression and incremental writes",
    "Unified YES-token perspective in quant.parquet for clean market analysis",
    "User-level split records with signed amounts for PnL and behavioral studies"
  ],
